{"type":null,"faqId":44891,"title":"为何语音唤醒时屏幕会亮，无其他响应？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">语音唤醒找手机需要您先说“唤醒词+命令词”才能完成。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">以默认唤醒词（你好小E）为例，如果仅仅说唤醒词（你好小E）只是完成唤醒动作，屏幕会亮，而不会响应命令词。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">加上命令词就可以完整执行命令，举例如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果找手机你需要说：你好小E，你在哪</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果打电话你需要说：你好小E，打电话给XXX。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"392","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409278000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":9,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"没有用,只能亮,没反应","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}